\b DR Screening AI Tool - Technology Stack Document\b0\par
\par
\b Project Summary\b0\par
This document explains the technology stack used in the DR Screening AI Tool, why each technology is used, and why it is the best fit for this project.\par
\par
\b Tech Stack Table\b0\par
\par
\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl\b Layer\b0\cell\b Technology\b0\cell\b Why We Use It\b0\cell\b Why It Is Best for Our Work\b0\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl API Backend\cell FastAPI\cell To create DR and quality prediction APIs\cell High performance, async support, lightweight architecture\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl API Server\cell Uvicorn\cell To run FastAPI as ASGI server\cell Fast startup and production-friendly runtime\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl Deep Learning\cell PyTorch (torch)\cell For model training and inference\cell Flexible, reliable, and strong for medical vision workflows\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl Vision Models\cell torchvision (EfficientNet B0/B3)\cell For pretrained models and transforms\cell Great accuracy-speed balance for retinal image classification\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl Image Processing\cell Pillow (PIL)\cell To read, convert, and save images\cell Stable and standard Python image processing library\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl Numerical Computing\cell NumPy\cell Array and numeric operations\cell Fast operations and easy integration with ML stack\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl Explainable AI\cell pytorch-grad-cam\cell To generate model heatmaps\cell Improves trust and interpretability in medical predictions\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl File Upload\cell python-multipart\cell To support API image upload\cell Standard, reliable FastAPI-compatible upload support\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl DB Connectivity\cell pyodbc\cell To connect Python service with SQL Server\cell Enterprise-friendly integration on Windows ecosystem\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl Database\cell Microsoft SQL Server\cell To store predictions, quality logs, and audit data\cell Reliable, structured, and reporting/audit ready\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl Model Files\cell .pt checkpoints\cell To deploy trained DR and quality models\cell Fast loading with reproducible inference behavior\cell\row

\trowd\trgaph108\trleft0
\cellx1800\cellx4200\cellx7600\cellx11200
\intbl Training Utility\cell scikit-learn (class weights)\cell To handle class imbalance\cell Better learning for minority DR severity classes\cell\row

\par
\b Why This Complete Stack Works Best\b0\par
- End-to-end flow: upload -> quality screening -> DR prediction -> explanation -> logging\par
- Balanced performance and accuracy with EfficientNet models\par
- Explainability through Grad-CAM for clinical confidence\par
- SQL-backed audit trail for traceability and reporting\par
- Easy scaling from PoC to production deployment\par
\par
